              <td style="padding: 8px 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: center;"><strong>全世帯4ヶ月無料</strong></td>
              <td style="padding: 8px 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: center;">福祉減免のみ</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
